CommentBody: Preflight done and all files and images uploaded to ticket.

The upgrade to 11.6 NEA was successful, however we found a problem with missing files that prevents us from editing the config on the ADI scans. We upgraded NEA in our labs internally and found the same issue so an escalation is being opened.

When attempting to upgrade AIC, we found that the DB was inaccessible, the customer is going to work to get the credentials for the DB as they did not have them immediately available, once they have this they will reschedule a meeting and we can complete the AIC upgrade.
